[
  {
    "id": "kp-6.1-01",
    "section": "6.1",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Histograms",
    "title_zh": "直方图",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "**Histograms** are used to represent continuous data, particularly when class widths are unequal. Unlike bar charts, the area of the bar represents the frequency, not the height.\n\n**Frequency density** is the vertical axis of a histogram. It is calculated using the formula: $\\text{Frequency density} = \\frac{\\text{Frequency}}{\\text{Class width}}$.\n\n**Area and Frequency** relationship is fundamental: $\\text{Frequency} = \\text{Frequency density} \\times \\text{Class width}$. To find the total frequency from a histogram, you must calculate and sum the areas of all the bars.",
      "zh": "**直方图** (Histograms) 用于表示连续数据，特别是在组距（class widths）不等的情况下。与条形图不同，直方图中条形的面积代表频数，而不是高度。\n\n**频数密度** (Frequency density) 是直方图的纵轴。其计算公式为：$\\text{频数密度} = \\frac{\\text{频数}}{\\text{组距}}$。\n\n**面积与频数**的关系是核心：$\\text{频数} = \\text{频数密度} \\times \\text{组距}$。要从直方图中找出总频数，必须计算并累加所有条形的面积。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-draw-histogram",
        "label": "Drawing a histogram from a frequency table",
        "label_zh": "根据频数表绘制直方图",
        "description": "Calculate frequency densities for each class and draw bars with heights corresponding to these densities.",
        "description_zh": "计算每组的频数密度，并绘制高度对应这些密度的条形。"
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-read-histogram",
        "label": "Calculating frequency from a histogram",
        "label_zh": "从直方图中计算频数",
        "description": "Use the area of bars (width $\\times$ height) to find missing frequencies or total values.",
        "description_zh": "利用条形的面积（宽度 $\\times$ 高度）来计算缺失的频数或总量。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-draw-histogram",
        "question": "A table shows the weights of 40 parcels. For the class $0 < w \\leq 10$, the frequency is 15. For $10 < w \\leq 25$, the frequency is 12. Calculate the frequency density for both classes.",
        "question_zh": "下表显示了40个包裹的重量。对于 $0 < w \\leq 10$ 组，频数为15。对于 $10 < w \\leq 25$ 组，频数为12。计算这两组的频数密度。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Identify class widths.\nFor $0 < w \\leq 10$, width = $10 - 0 = 10$.\nFor $10 < w \\leq 25$, width = $25 - 10 = 15$.\n\n**Step 2:** Apply the formula $\\text{FD} = \\frac{\\text{Frequency}}{\\text{Width}}$.\nFD for first class = $\\frac{15}{10} = 1.5$.\nFD for second class = $\\frac{12}{15} = 0.8$.\n\n**Answers:** 1.5 and 0.8",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 确定组距。\n对于 $0 < w \\leq 10$，组距 = $10 - 0 = 10$。\n对于 $10 < w \\leq 25$，组距 = $25 - 10 = 15$。\n\n**步骤2：** 使用公式 $\\text{FD} = \\frac{\\text{频数}}{\\text{组距}}$。\n第一组的频数密度 = $\\frac{15}{10} = 1.5$。\n第二组的频数密度 = $\\frac{12}{15} = 0.8$。\n\n**答案：** 1.5 和 0.8",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1H/Jan/2021"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-read-histogram",
        "question": "In a histogram, the bar for $20 < x \\leq 30$ has a frequency density of 4.2. Calculate the frequency of this class.",
        "question_zh": "在直方图中，$20 < x \\leq 30$ 组条形的频数密度为 4.2。计算该组的频数。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Calculate class width.\nWidth = $30 - 20 = 10$.\n\n**Step 2:** Calculate frequency using area.\n$\\text{Frequency} = \\text{Width} \\times \\text{Frequency Density}$\n$\\text{Frequency} = 10 \\times 4.2 = 42$.\n\n**Answer:** 42",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 计算组距。\n组距 = $30 - 20 = 10$。\n\n**步骤2：** 利用面积计算频数。\n$\\text{频数} = \\text{组距} \\times \\text{频数密度}$\n$\\text{频数} = 10 \\times 4.2 = 42$。\n\n**答案：** 42",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2H/June/2020"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "What does the vertical axis represent in a histogram?",
        "q_zh": "在直方图中，纵轴代表什么？",
        "o": [
          "Frequency",
          "Cumulative Frequency",
          "Frequency Density",
          "Class Width"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "In a histogram, the vertical axis is always frequency density. Frequency is represented by the area of the bars.",
        "e_zh": "在直方图中，纵轴始终是频数密度。频数由条形的面积表示。"
      },
      {
        "q": "If a bar has a width of 5 and represents a frequency of 20, what is its height on the histogram?",
        "q_zh": "如果一个条形的宽度为5，代表的频数为20，那么它在直方图上的高度是多少？",
        "o": [
          "100",
          "4",
          "0.25",
          "15"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "Height = Frequency Density = Frequency / Width = $20 / 5 = 4$.",
        "e_zh": "高度 = 频数密度 = 频数 / 组距 = $20 / 5 = 4$。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [],
    "tier": "higher"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-6.1-02",
    "section": "6.1",
    "order": 2,
    "title": "Cumulative Frequency and Box Plots",
    "title_zh": "累积频数与箱线图",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "**Cumulative frequency** is the running total of frequencies. It is plotted at the **upper class boundary** of each interval to create a cumulative frequency graph.\n\n**Median and Quartiles** can be estimated from the graph. The median ($Q_2$) is at the $\\frac{n}{2}$ position, the lower quartile ($Q_1$) is at $\\frac{n}{4}$, and the upper quartile ($Q_3$) is at $\\frac{3n}{4}$.\n\n**Box plots** (or box-and-whisker diagrams) are a visual summary of the five-number summary: minimum, lower quartile, median, upper quartile, and maximum. The **Interquartile Range (IQR)** is $Q_3 - Q_1$, representing the spread of the middle 50% of the data.",
      "zh": "**累积频数** (Cumulative frequency) 是频数的逐项累加。在绘制累积频数图时，点应标在每个组限的**上限**处。\n\n**中位数与四分位数**可以通过图形估算。中位数 ($Q_2$) 位于 $\\frac{n}{2}$ 处，下四分位数 ($Q_1$) 位于 $\\frac{n}{4}$ 处，上四分位数 ($Q_3$) 位于 $\\frac{3n}{4}$ 处。\n\n**箱线图** (Box plots) 是五数概括法的视觉总结：最小值、下四分位数、中位数、上四分位数和最大值。**四分位距 (IQR)** 为 $Q_3 - Q_1$，代表中间 50% 数据的离散程度。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-estimate-cf",
        "label": "Estimating statistics from a CF graph",
        "label_zh": "从累积频数图中估算统计量",
        "description": "Find the median, quartiles, or the number of values above/below a certain point.",
        "description_zh": "找出中位数、四分位数，或高于/低于某一点的数值个数。"
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-compare-boxplots",
        "label": "Comparing distributions using box plots",
        "label_zh": "使用箱线图比较分布",
        "description": "Compare two data sets using the median (average) and IQR (consistency/spread).",
        "description_zh": "使用中位数（平均水平）和四分位距（一致性/离散度）比较两组数据。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-estimate-cf",
        "question": "A cumulative frequency curve is drawn for 80 students' marks. From the graph, the 20th value is 35, the 40th value is 52, and the 60th value is 71. State the median and find the IQR.",
        "question_zh": "绘制了80名学生成绩的累积频数曲线。从图中可知，第20个值是35，第40个值是52，第60个值是71。写出中位数并求四分位距 (IQR)。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** The median is the $\\frac{80}{2} = 40$th value.\nMedian = 52.\n\n**Step 2:** Find the quartiles.\n$Q_1$ (lower quartile) = $\\frac{80}{4} = 20$th value = 35.\n$Q_3$ (upper quartile) = $\\frac{3 \\times 80}{4} = 60$th value = 71.\n\n**Step 3:** Calculate IQR.\n$IQR = Q_3 - Q_1 = 71 - 35 = 36$.\n\n**Answers:** Median = 52, IQR = 36",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 中位数是第 $\\frac{80}{2} = 40$ 个值。\n中位数 = 52。\n\n**步骤2：** 找出四分位数。\n$Q_1$ (下四分位数) = 第 $\\frac{80}{4} = 20$ 个值 = 35。\n$Q_3$ (上四分位数) = 第 $\\frac{3 \\times 80}{4} = 60$ 个值 = 71。\n\n**步骤3：** 计算 IQR。\n$IQR = Q_3 - Q_1 = 71 - 35 = 36$。\n\n**答案：** 中位数 = 52, IQR = 36",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2H/June/2019"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-compare-boxplots",
        "question": "Two box plots show the heights of girls and boys. Girls: Median = 155cm, IQR = 10cm. Boys: Median = 162cm, IQR = 15cm. Compare the distributions.",
        "question_zh": "两张箱线图显示了女孩和男孩的身高。女孩：中位数 = 155cm，IQR = 10cm。男孩：中位数 = 162cm，IQR = 15cm。比较这两组分布。",
        "solution": "1. **Compare average:** The boys are taller on average because their median (162cm) is higher than the girls' median (155cm).\n2. **Compare spread:** The girls' heights are more consistent (less spread out) because their IQR (10cm) is smaller than the boys' IQR (15cm).",
        "solution_zh": "1. **比较平均水平：** 男孩平均更高，因为他们的中位数 (162cm) 高于女孩的中位数 (155cm)。\n2. **比较离散度：** 女孩的身高更一致（离散度更小），因为她们的 IQR (10cm) 小于男孩的 IQR (15cm)。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "Where should points be plotted on a cumulative frequency graph?",
        "q_zh": "在累积频数图中，点应该标在何处？",
        "o": [
          "Midpoint of the class",
          "Lower class boundary",
          "Upper class boundary",
          "Frequency density"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "Cumulative frequency represents the total frequency 'up to' a certain value, so it must be plotted at the upper class boundary.",
        "e_zh": "累积频数代表“直到”某个值的总频数，因此必须标在组限的上限处。"
      },
      {
        "q": "What does a smaller Interquartile Range (IQR) indicate about a data set?",
        "q_zh": "较小的四分位距 (IQR) 说明数据集的什么特征？",
        "o": [
          "The data is higher on average",
          "The data is more spread out",
          "The data is more consistent",
          "The data has a higher maximum"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "A smaller IQR means the middle 50% of the data is closer together, indicating greater consistency or less spread.",
        "e_zh": "较小的 IQR 意味着中间 50% 的数据更接近，表明数据更一致或离散度更小。"
      }
    ],
