    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-6.2-01",
    "section": "6.2",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Mean for Grouped Data",
    "title_zh": "分组数据的平均数",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "When data is grouped in a frequency table, we don't know the exact values. We use the **midpoint** of each class as an estimate for all values in that class.\n\nTo find the **estimate of the mean** ($\\bar{x}$):\n1. Find the **midpoint** ($x$) of each class interval.\n2. Multiply each midpoint by its corresponding **frequency** ($f$) to get $f \\times x$.\n3. Sum all the $fx$ values ($\\sum fx$).\n4. Divide by the **total frequency** ($n$ or $\\sum f$).\n\nFormula: $\\text{Mean} \\approx \\frac{\\sum (f \\times x)}{\\sum f}$",
      "zh": "当数据在频数表中分组时，我们不知道确切的数值。我们使用每组的**中点** (midpoint) 作为该组所有数值的估算值。\n\n计算**平均数估算值** ($\\bar{x}$) 的步骤：\n1. 找出每个组区间的**中点** ($x$)。\n2. 将每个中点乘以其对应的**频数** ($f$)，得到 $f \\times x$。\n3. 将所有 $fx$ 值求和 ($\\sum fx$)。\n4. 除以**总频数** ($n$ 或 $\\sum f$)。\n\n公式：$\\text{平均数} \\approx \\frac{\\sum (f \\times x)}{\\sum f}$"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-calc-mean-grouped",
        "label": "Calculate estimate of the mean",
        "label_zh": "计算平均数估算值",
        "description": "Given a table of grouped data, find the midpoints and calculate the mean.",
        "description_zh": "给出分组数据表，找出中点并计算平均数。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-calc-mean-grouped",
        "question": "Find the estimate for the mean of the following data:\n\n| Height ($h$ cm) | Frequency ($f$) |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| $140 < h \\leq 150$ | 4 |\n| $150 < h \\leq 160$ | 10 |\n| $160 < h \\leq 170$ | 6 |",
        "question_zh": "计算下列数据的平均数估算值：\n\n| 身高 ($h$ cm) | 频数 ($f$) |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| $140 < h \\leq 150$ | 4 |\n| $150 < h \\leq 160$ | 10 |\n| $160 < h \\leq 170$ | 6 |",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Find midpoints ($x$): 145, 155, 165.\n\n**Step 2:** Calculate $f \\times x$:\n$4 \\times 145 = 580$\n$10 \\times 155 = 1550$\n$6 \\times 165 = 990$\n\n**Step 3:** Sum frequencies and $fx$ values:\n$\\sum f = 4 + 10 + 6 = 20$\n$\\sum fx = 580 + 1550 + 990 = 3120$\n\n**Step 4:** Divide:\nMean = $3120 / 20 = 156$.\n\n**Answer:** 156 cm",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 找出中点 ($x$)：145, 155, 165。\n\n**步骤2：** 计算 $f \\times x$：\n$4 \\times 145 = 580$\n$10 \\times 155 = 1550$\n$6 \\times 165 = 990$\n\n**步骤3：** 对频数和 $fx$ 值求和：\n$\\sum f = 4 + 10 + 6 = 20$\n$\\sum fx = 580 + 1550 + 990 = 3120$\n\n**步骤4：** 相除：\n平均数 = $3120 / 20 = 156$。\n\n**答案：** 156 cm",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1F/Jan/2020"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-calc-mean-grouped",
        "question": "A frequency table has a modal class. If the classes are $0-10, 10-20, 20-30$ with frequencies $5, 12, 8$, which class is the modal class?",
        "question_zh": "一个频数表有众数组。如果各组为 $0-10, 10-20, 20-30$，频数分别为 $5, 12, 8$，哪一组是众数组？",
        "solution": "The **modal class** is the class with the highest frequency.\nFrequency 12 is the highest.\nThe corresponding class is $10-20$.\n\n**Answer:** $10-20$",
        "solution_zh": "**众数组** (Modal class) 是频数最高的组。\n频数 12 是最高的。\n对应的组是 $10-20$。\n\n**答案：** $10-20$",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "Why is the mean from a grouped frequency table called an 'estimate'?",
        "q_zh": "为什么分组频率表的平均数被称为“估算值”？",
        "o": [
          "Because the calculation is rounded",
          "Because we don't know the exact values within each class",
          "Because the total frequency might be wrong",
          "Because midpoints are not real numbers"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "We use midpoints because the raw data values are unknown, making the final result an estimate rather than an exact mean.",
        "e_zh": "我们使用中点是因为原始数据值未知，这使得最终结果是估算值而非精确平均数。"
      },
      {
        "q": "What is the midpoint of the class interval $25 < x \\leq 40$?",
        "q_zh": "组区间 $25 < x \\leq 40$ 的中点是多少？",
        "o": [
          "32",
          "33",
          "32.5",
          "15"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "Midpoint = $(25 + 40) / 2 = 65 / 2 = 32.5$.",
        "e_zh": "中点 = $(25 + 40) / 2 = 65 / 2 = 32.5$。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-6.3-01",
    "section": "6.3",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Combined Events and Tree Diagrams",
    "title_zh": "复合事件与树状图",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "**Combined events** involve two or more actions (e.g., flipping a coin twice). The total probability of all possible outcomes always sums to 1.\n\n**Tree diagrams** are used to calculate probabilities for multiple stages:\n1. **Multiply** probabilities along the branches to find the probability of a specific sequence of outcomes (AND rule).\n2. **Add** the probabilities of different branches if more than one outcome satisfies the condition (OR rule).\n\n**Replacement:** If an object is replaced, probabilities remain the same for the second event (independent). If **not replaced**, the total number of outcomes and the count of specific items decrease (dependent).",
      "zh": "**复合事件**涉及两个或更多动作（例如，掷两次硬币）。所有可能结果的总概率始终等于1。\n\n**树状图**用于计算多个阶段的概率：\n1. 沿分支**相乘**概率，以找出特定结果序列的概率（“且”规则）。\n2. 如果有多个结果满足条件，将不同分支的概率**相加**（“或”规则）。\n\n**放回与不放回：** 如果物体被放回，第二次事件的概率保持不变（独立事件）。如果**不放回**，总结果数和特定物品的数量都会减少（相关事件）。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-tree-diagram",
        "label": "Completing and using tree diagrams",
        "label_zh": "完成并使用树状图",
        "description": "Fill in missing probabilities on branches and calculate the probability of combined outcomes.",
        "description_zh": "填写分支上缺失的概率，并计算复合结果的概率。"
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-without-replacement",
        "label": "Probability without replacement",
        "label_zh": "不放回抽样的概率",
        "description": "Handle changes in denominators and numerators for sequential events.",
        "description_zh": "处理连续事件中分母和分子的变化。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-tree-diagram",
        "question": "A bag contains 7 blue and 3 red counters. Two counters are taken at random with replacement. Calculate the probability that both counters are red.",
        "question_zh": "一个袋子里有7个蓝色和3个红色筹码。随机取出两个筹码，有放回。计算两个筹码都是红色的概率。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Probability of Red on 1st pick = $\\frac{3}{10}$.\n\n**Step 2:** Since it is with replacement, Probability of Red on 2nd pick = $\\frac{3}{10}$.\n\n**Step 3:** Multiply for 'Red AND Red'.\n$P(RR) = \\frac{3}{10} \\times \\frac{3}{10} = \\frac{9}{100}$.\n\n**Answer:** 0.09",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 第一次取到红色的概率 = $\\frac{3}{10}$。\n\n**步骤2：** 因为是有放回，第二次取到红色的概率 = $\\frac{3}{10}$。\n\n**步骤3：** 将“红色且红色”的概率相乘。\n$P(RR) = \\frac{3}{10} \\times \\frac{3}{10} = \\frac{9}{100}$。\n\n**答案：** 0.09",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2F/Jan/2021"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-without-replacement",
        "question": "A box contains 5 green and 4 yellow sweets. Two sweets are taken without replacement. Find the probability that they are different colors.",
        "question_zh": "盒子里有5个绿色和4个黄色糖果。不放回地取出两个糖果。求它们颜色不同的概率。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Identify paths for different colors: (Green, Yellow) OR (Yellow, Green).\n\n**Step 2:** Calculate $P(GY)$:\n$\\frac{5}{9} \\times \\frac{4}{8} = \\frac{20}{72}$.\n\n**Step 3:** Calculate $P(YG)$:\n$\\frac{4}{9} \\times \\frac{5}{8} = \\frac{20}{72}$.\n\n**Step 4:** Add the probabilities:\n$\\frac{20}{72} + \\frac{20}{72} = \\frac{40}{72} = \\frac{5}{9}$.\n\n**Answer:** $\\frac{5}{9}$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 确定颜色不同的路径：(绿, 黄) 或 (黄, 绿)。\n\n**步骤2：** 计算 $P(绿黄)$：\n$\\frac{5}{9} \\times \\frac{4}{8} = \\frac{20}{72}$。\n\n**步骤3：** 计算 $P(黄绿)$：\n$\\frac{4}{9} \\times \\frac{5}{8} = \\frac{20}{72}$。\n\n**步骤4：** 将概率相加：\n$\\frac{20}{72} + \\frac{20}{72} = \\frac{40}{72} = \\frac{5}{9}$。\n\n**答案：** $\\frac{5}{9}$",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1H/June/2019"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "If $P(A) = 0.3$ and $P(B) = 0.4$, and they are independent, what is $P(A \\text{ and } B)$?",
        "q_zh": "如果 $P(A) = 0.3$，$P(B) = 0.4$，且它们是独立事件，那么 $P(A \\text{ 且 } B)$ 是多少？",
        "o": [
          "0.7",
          "0.12",
          "0.1",
          "0.75"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "For independent events, $P(A \\cap B) = P(A) \\times P(B) = 0.3 \\times 0.4 = 0.12$.",
        "e_zh": "对于独立事件，$P(A \\cap B) = P(A) \\times P(B) = 0.3 \\times 0.4 = 0.12$。"
      },
      {
        "q": "In a tree diagram, what must the probabilities on any set of branches from a single point sum to?",
        "q_zh": "在树状图中，从单一点出发的一组分支的概率之和必须是多少？",
        "o": [
          "0",
          "0.5",
          "1",
          "100"
        ],
