        "patternId": "ep-venn-prob",
        "question": "In a Venn diagram, circle A contains 10 elements, circle B contains 15 elements, and their intersection contains 4 elements. There are 30 elements in total. Find $P(A|B)$.",
        "question_zh": "在韦恩图中，圆 A 包含 10 个元素，圆 B 包含 15 个元素，它们的交集包含 4 个元素。总共有 30 个元素。求 $P(A|B)$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Identify $P(A \\cap B)$ and $P(B)$.\nNumber of elements in $A \\cap B = 4$.\nNumber of elements in $B = 15$.\n\n**Step 2:** Apply the conditional probability formula.\n$P(A|B) = \\frac{\\text{Number in } A \\cap B}{\\text{Number in } B} = \\frac{4}{15}$.\n\n**Answer:** $\\frac{4}{15}$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 确定 $A \\cap B$ 和 $B$ 的元素数。\n$A \\cap B$ 的元素数 = 4。\n$B$ 的元素数 = 15。\n\n**步骤2：** 应用条件概率公式。\n$P(A|B) = \\frac{A \\cap B \\text{ 的数量}}{B \\text{ 的数量}} = \\frac{4}{15}$。\n\n**答案：** $\\frac{4}{15}$",
