      {
        "patternId": "ep-conditional-logic",
        "question": "Given $P(X) = 0.6$, $P(Y) = 0.5$ and $P(X \\cup Y) = 0.8$. Calculate $P(X|Y)$.",
        "question_zh": "已知 $P(X) = 0.6$，$P(Y) = 0.5$ 且 $P(X \\cup Y) = 0.8$。计算 $P(X|Y)$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Find $P(X \\cap Y)$ using the formula $P(X \\cup Y) = P(X) + P(Y) - P(X \\cap Y)$.\n$0.8 = 0.6 + 0.5 - P(X \\cap Y)$\n$0.8 = 1.1 - P(X \\cap Y)$\n$P(X \\cap Y) = 0.3$.\n\n**Step 2:** Calculate $P(X|Y)$.\n$P(X|Y) = \\frac{P(X \\cap Y)}{P(Y)} = \\frac{0.3}{0.5} = 0.6$.\n\n**Answer:** 0.6",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 使用公式 $P(X \\cup Y) = P(X) + P(Y) - P(X \\cap Y)$ 找出 $P(X \\cap Y)$。\n$0.8 = 0.6 + 0.5 - P(X \\cap Y)$\n$0.8 = 1.1 - P(X \\cap Y)$\n$P(X \\cap Y) = 0.3$。\n\n**步骤2：** 计算 $P(X|Y)$。\n$P(X|Y) = \\frac{P(X \\cap Y)}{P(Y)} = \\frac{0.3}{0.5} = 0.6$。\n\n**答案：** 0.6",
